VASSAL.build.module.documentation

Class BrowserHelpFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • VASSAL.build.AbstractBuildable
      • VASSAL.build.module.documentation.BrowserHelpFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Buildable, Configurable, PropertyNameSource, ValidityChecker, Translatable

    public class BrowserHelpFile
extends AbstractBuildable
implements Configurable
    Unpacks a zipped directory stored in the module and displays it in an external browser window.
